        <p>To use the eraser, click  <img src="../../../../Images/eraser2_btn.png" alt="" title="" class="ReduceButtonSize" /> in the Edit ribbon or the local toolbar of the Capture Editor.</p>
        <p>The eraser allows you to erase any part of a background image. You can change the size of the eraser using a slider in the local toolbar of the Capture Editor <img src="../../../../Images/eraser_and_pencil_sizer_btn.png" class="ReduceButtonSize"></img>. Move the slider to the right to make the eraser larger, or move it to the left to make it smaller.</p>
